<paragraph id="8E58180576C0766BBB0441DA25BA53C0" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">In the Nearctic Region, this is a western species that has been collected west of the Sierra/Cascade cordillera in the states of Oregon and Washington and in the province of British Columbia.</paragraph>
